*******************************************

Project 1 - CS 371

PACKET SNIFFER

*******************************************

About

*******************************************

This program uses the Libpcap library to 
"sniff" incoming and outgoing TCP and UDP 
packets from the local host.

*******************************************

Usage

*******************************************

Compile the program:

>>gcc -Wall -pedantic sniffer2_1.c -lpcap

Run the program:

>> ./a.out

*******************************************

Results from the Packet Sniffer are found
in the following files created by the
program and put in the working directory

--datapersec.txt
--pktspersec.txt
--ipaddress.txt
--ports.txt
--tcpvsudp.txt
*******************************************
